Heyo guys - I'm writing an extensive piece for <http://lemlist.com|lemlist.com>
(DR61 - sales-related blog) on the lead qualification best practices.

I'm accepting 100 - 200 word contributions. You get mention and backlink.

What I need is some of the following:
- How are you doing lead qualification at your company?
- What is your NO. 1 tip for sales qualification?
- How are you doing your lead scoring?
- How are you doing discovery calls?

You can send me your contribution on <mailto:ugi@lemlist.com|ugi@lemlist.com>. Please put the subject line of the email as following (so I won't miss it): "[Full Name] - Lead qualification contribution"
Deadline: Wednesday 12pm Central European Time
